籤詩版本二:
E faigata tele ona tauivi mo le manuia, ae o aso o le tauivi mo faaipoipoga e pisi mo sina taimi.
I le iʻuga, e lavea o ia i le aū, e taʻitaʻia e le tagata mamalu le nuu.
詩意:
O lenei hexagram o loʻo faʻatusalia ai se faʻamanuiaga i le faʻaogaina.
E manuia mea uma.
解曰: Suiga ma le loto i ai. Enron i le faaiuga. Afai e te fesili e uiga i le faʻaaogaina. Na o le latalata i tagata tamalii.
籤詩故事一:
◇ Fautuaga Tusi Jiang Wei (Fautuaga Tusi Jiang Wei)
Jiang Wei (202-264), igoa fa'aaloalo Boyue, o se tagatanuu o Ji County, Tianshui County, Liangzhou (lea Gangu County, Tianshui City, Gansu Province).
I le vaitaimi o Malo e Tolu, na ta'ita'ia faono e Kong Ming 'au mai Qishan e osofa'i Cao Wei. Sa ma'i tigaina Kong Ming ma sa matua tigaina lava. Na ia aoao atu mataupu e luasefulufa o le Tusi o Taua i le taitai aoao o Jiang Wei, ma le faamoemoe e mafai ona ia maua lona tofi.
(O le faʻataʻitaʻiga o lenei tala e faapea o Jiang Wei na tuufaasolo mo nisi mafuaaga)
聖意: Manuia mo le aiga, manuia, pisinisi, faaipoipoga, Liujia, tane savali e lei taunuu mai, Tiansi Zhongping, Liu manu lafulemu, Zhongping, saili mo tagata, faamasinoga lautele, femalagaiga talafeagai, leiloa meatotino, faamaʻi i Sasae, Xingxingshan tuugamau auspicious
古人: Fautuaga Tusi ia Jiang Wei (Tusi ia Jiang Wei)
